        {
          "title": "Ferrari",
          "year": 2023,
          "note": "Michael Mann's biopic narrows to a few months of 1957: the money running out, the marriage to Laura (Penélope Cruz) coming apart after their son Dino's death, a second family with Lena (Shailene Woodley), and the Mille Miglia ahead. Sean and Chris both loved it, with Chris calling Adam Driver's Enzo the best performance he saw all year; Amanda liked it but found Woodley miscast. Adapted from Brock Yates's book; Christian Bale and later Hugh Jackman were once attached to the lead. Also with Sarah Gadon, Gabriel Leone, Jack O'Connell, and Patrick Dempsey."
        }
